 If you want U{OPeNDAP<http://opendap.org/>} support, add 'C{--enable-dap}'.
 If you want HDF4 SD support, add 'C{--enable-hdf4}' and add
 the location of the HDF4 headers and library to C{CPPFLAGS} and C{LDFLAGS}.


